Important:

Do not start backend from repo root with backend.app.main:app
Start from backend directory with app.main:app
Keep both backend and frontend terminals running at the same time

If you see "[Errno 48] Address already in use":

That means a backend instance is already running on port 8000.
If this command returns 200, backend is already healthy and you do not need to start it again:
curl -sS -o /dev/null -w "%{http_code}\n" http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs

Only restart backend if needed.
Find it:
lsof -nP -iTCP:8000 -sTCP:LISTEN

Stop it (safe if no PID is found):
lsof -ti tcp:8000 | xargs kill -9

Then start backend again from backend directory:
cd /Users/brendanduffy/Documents/FinancialModeling/backend
source ../.venv/bin/activate
uvicorn app.main:app --reload --port 8000